Privacy Policy for Bible Verses 4 Situations Pro
Effective Date: December 1, 2024

This Privacy Policy applies to the Bible Verses 4 Situations Pro app, developed by Maryjane21 ("we," "our," or "us"). Your privacy is our top priority. This document explains how the app handles your information in compliance with Google Play's Developer Program Policies.


---

1. Purpose and Scope

This privacy policy applies exclusively to the Bible Verses 4 Situations Pro app (com.sacredspace.bibleversesforeverysituationpro) as listed on Google Play.


---

2. No Data Collection

Our app is designed to operate offline. We do not collect, store, process, or share any personal or sensitive user data such as your name, email address, or location.


---

3. App Permissions

The app may request the following permissions to function effectively:

Push Notifications: The app may request permission to send daily Bible verse notifications. These notifications are managed locally on your device and do not involve any external data collection or transmission.

Storage Access (if applicable): The app may request access to your device’s storage for saving or loading Bible verse files. However, no data is uploaded or shared externally.


You can manage or revoke these permissions at any time through your device settings.


---

4. No Third-Party Services

We do not use third-party services, analytics, advertising platforms, or external APIs. This ensures that no data is shared with third parties.


---

5. Data Security

Although the app does not collect data, we are committed to providing a secure and private experience. The app is built to minimize risks by not transmitting any information over the internet.


---

6. Children’s Privacy

The Bible Verses 4 Situations Pro app is suitable for all ages, including children. Since we do not collect or store any personal information, the app complies with privacy protection laws for children, such as COPPA (Children's Online Privacy Protection Act).


---

7. Data Retention and Deletion Policy

As the app does not collect or store user data, there is no retention or deletion process required.


---

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We may occasionally update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our app or relevant regulations. Any changes will be posted here, with the effective date updated accordingly.


---

9. Contact Us

For privacy-related questions, concerns, or requests, please contact us at:

Maryjane21
Email: sacredspacewiththelord@gmail.com

We are committed to addressing your inquiries promptly.


---

Last Updated: December 6, 2024
